s=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>useState 를 호출한다는 것은 “state” 라는 변수를 선언하는 것과 같으며, 이 변수의 이름은 아무 이름으로 지어도 된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"️-props\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-props\" aria-label=\"️ props permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔️ Props</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>외부로부터 전달받은 값</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>함부로 변경될 수 없는 읽기 전용 객체</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"react-데이터-흐름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"react 데이터 흐름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React 데이터 흐름</h3>\n<h4 id=\"️-상향식으로-앱을-만들기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-%EC%83%81%ED%96%A5%EC%8B%9D%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%95%B1%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"️ 상향식으로 앱을 만들기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-